The paper focuses on characterizing data analysis workloads in data centers, which involves understanding their micro-architectural characteristics and optimizing system performance. This falls under the categories of computer architecture (cs.AR), databases (cs.DB), distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC), software engineering (cs.SE), and systems and control (cs.SY).
